---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Chinese History" description="Explore 5,000 years of Chinese history - dynasties, emperors, inventions, and the fascinating stories that shaped civilization.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-600 via-orange-700 to-amber-800 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="text-amber-200 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">History</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Chinese History</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-amber-100">From the mythic Xia Dynasty to the modern People's Republic, China's history is the longest continuous civilization on Earth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/history/dynasties" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏛️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Dynasties</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">From Qin to Qing—the rise and fall of imperial China across 2,000 years.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/history/figures" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">👑</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Historical Figures</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Emperors, philosophers, generals, and rebels who shaped China's destiny.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/history/inventions" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔥</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Inventions</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">Paper, printing, gunpowder, compass—the four great gifts to humanity.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/history/modern" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏮</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Modern China</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">The transformation from empire to republic to global power.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-8">Featured Articles</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">📖</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">The Tang Dynasty: China's Golden Age</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">How a dynasty born from chaos created the most cosmopolitan civilization in the world.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-yellow-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">⚔️</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">The Three Kingdoms: Fact vs Fiction</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Separating history from the legendary Romance of the Three Kingdoms.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="group">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-stone-500 to-stone-700 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl">🏯</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">The Great Wall: Myths and Reality</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">What the Wall really was, who built it, and why it matters today.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
